    "description": "<div style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:1.6;color:#222;max-width:800px;margin:0 auto\" vocab=\"https://schema.org/\" typeof=\"Product\">\n  <div style=\"display:none\"><span property=\"description\">Whether sewing, quilting, pattern making for fashion design or working with upholstery fabric and more, these fabric scissors will see you through countless cuts with precision, including cutting through multiple layers of fabric simultaneously with their classic dressmaking knife edge blades</span></div>\n  <div style=\"background:#f5f5f5;padding:12px 15px;border:1px solid #e5e5e5;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <div style=\"font-size:18px;font-weight:bold;margin-bottom:6px\">Deals Only Web Store</div>\n    <div style=\"font-size:13px\">\n      <a href=\"https://www.ebay.com/str/dealsonlywebstore\" style=\"text-decoration:none;color:#333\">Our Store</a>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <h2 style=\"font-size:22px;margin:0 0 12px\">ToolTreaux Stainless Steel Heavy Duty Fabric Scissors Sewing Supplies (3 Sizes)</h2>\n  <p>Whether sewing, quilting, pattern making for fashion design or working with upholstery fabric and more, these fabric scissors will see you through countless cuts with precision, including cutting through multiple layers of fabric simultaneously with their classic dressmaking knife edge blades.</p>\n  <p>- Angled bend in the handle and flat bottom guide or node allows the scissors or dressmakers shears to make contact with your cutting surface and remain flat for steadiness and precise cuts</p>\n  <h3 style=\"font-size:18px;margin:18px 0 8px\">Key Features</h3>\n  <ul style=\"padding-left:20px;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <li><strong>HEAVY DUTY FABRIC SCISSORS:</strong> Whether sewing, quilting, pattern making for fashion design or working with upholstery fabric and more, these heavy duty fabric scissors will see you through countless cuts with accuracy, including cutting through multiple layers of fabric simultaneously with knife edge blades</li>\n    <li><strong>ESSENTIAL SEWING SUPPLIES ITEM:</strong> If you have a serial sewer in your life, they’ll love these professional high quality fabric scissors for the weight, comfort and accuracy; the angled bend in the handle and flat bottom guide allows the scissors to make contact with your cutting surface and remain flat for steadiness and comfort</li>\n    <li><strong>STAINLESS STEEL:</strong> High quality construction made from stainless steel, these tailor scissors are incredibly strong, durable, corrosion resistant and are designed to withstand lots of wear and tear; the ergonomic angles design of the handle promotes ease of handling when cutting</li>\n    <li><strong>ULTRA SHARP BLADE RETENTION:</strong> Even after working through difficult fabrics and hundreds of cuts, the fabric scissors with long knife edge blades will remain sharp, easily handling tough materials with ease and precision</li>\n    <li><strong>SPECIFICATIONS:</strong> Dimensions: 10 x 3 x 0.75 inches; Color: Silver; Material: Stainless Steel; Plastic Vinyl Storage Case: Included with Purchase</li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"text-align:center;margin:0 0 16px\"><img src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/DOWS_products/1000x1000/Hobby_Tools/SC67H_10in_tailor_scissors_detail_main.jpg\" alt=\"Whether sewing, quilting, pattern making for fashion design or working with upholstery fabric and more, these fabric scissors will see you through\" style=\"max-width:100%;width:600px;height:auto\"></p>\n  <h3 style=\"font-size:18px;margin:18px 0 8px\">Product Specifications</h3>\n  <ul style=\"padding-left:20px;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <li><strong>MPN:</strong> TTFSSS10IN</li>\n    <li><strong>UPC:</strong> 810058475312</li>\n    <li><strong>Color:</strong> Silver</li>\n  </ul>\n  <p>- The stainless steel tailor scissors are incredibly strong, durable, corrosion resistant and are designed to withstand lots of wear and tear; the knife edge blades allows the top edge to cut an acute angle which is purposefully designed to cut through fabric easier than regular craft scissors</p>\n  <p>- Even after working through difficult fabrics and hundreds of cuts, the fabric scissors with long knife edge blades will remain sharp, easily handling tough materials time and time again</p>\n  <p>- The fabric scissors also feature a tapered design on the top blade to prevent the sewing scissors from snagging on seams or threads; the more pointed tip is ideal for clipping and notching curves</p>\n  <p>If you have a serial sewer or fabric crafter in your life, or you’re just taking on some new sewing or fabric projects yourself, these professional, high-quality fabric scissors offer comfort and accuracy with each and every cut.</p>\n  <p style=\"text-align:center;margin:16px 0 0\"><img src=\"https://s3.us-east-1.amazonaws.com/DOWS_photobucket/Shopify_Prop65graphic.jpg\" alt=\"California Proposition 65 warning\" style=\"display:block;margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto\" height=\"78\" width=\"273\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:18px 0 0;padding-top:12px;border-top:1px solid #e5e5e5;font-size:13px;color:#777;text-align:center\">&copy; 2026 Deals Only Web Store</p>\n</div>",
